                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h1>Free email tracker for sales and customer managers</h1>
                        <h3>Know when and where your emails are opened. Integrate with tools you use everyday to manage your customers.</h3>
                        <p class="m-t-lg">
                            <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary m-t-md" target="_blank" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/contextsmith-email-tracke/idihnnlkpfggfgjinfiodninabjggfop" role="button">Install for Gmail</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
