            <div class="col-lg-4 features-text wow fadeInLeft">
                <h2>Track when and where your emails are read</h2>
                <p>With unlimited email tracking, you’ll know who opens your every email. It’s all valuable information to help you follow up with your leads or customers with more context.</p>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/contextsmith-email-tracke/idihnnlkpfggfgjinfiodninabjggfop" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Install for free</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8 text-right wow fadeInRight">
                <%= image_tag 'landing/landing_track.png', :class => "img-responsive pull-right", :alt => "email_tracker" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="features" style="background-color: #efefef">
        <div class="row features-block">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 features-text text-center m-b-lg">
                <h2>Insights on how your emails are performing</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 text-left wow fadeInLeft">
                <%= image_tag 'landing/landing_dashboard.png', :class => "img-responsive", :alt => "email_dashboard" %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center m-t-xl m-b-xl">
                <a target="_blank" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/contextsmith-email-tracke/idihnnlkpfggfgjinfiodninabjggfop" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Install for free</a>
