            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="features" style="background-color: #efefef;padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:40px;margin-top:50px">
        <div class="row container features-block">
            <div class="col-lg-4 features-text wow fadeInRight pull-right">
                <h2>Automatically log emails to any CRM, or use us as your CRM</h2>
                <p>Automatically BCC to your CRM or any email address.  No more spending weekends logging emails into CRM, and let us take care of that in real-time.</p>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/contextsmith-email-tracke/idihnnlkpfggfgjinfiodninabjggfop" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Install for free</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 col-lg-offset-1 text-left wow fadeInLeft">
